    {
      "index": 9,
      "indent": 0,
      "section": "Ambassador Spanfipple",
      "text": {
        "en": "Head back downstairs, go to the west stairs of the castle, go upstairs, and investigate the suit of armour. (The correct suits of armour in this step and following steps periodically say and are marked with a quest icon in their tooltip.)",
        "es": "Baja de nuevo, ve a las escaleras del oeste del castillo, sube y examina la armadura. (Las armaduras correctas en este paso y en los siguientes lo indican periódicamente y aparecen marcadas con un icono de misión en su descripción emergente.)"
      },
      "chatOptions": [],
      "highlightTerms": [
        "suit of armour"
      ]
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "indent": 0,
      "section": "Ambassador Spanfipple",
      "text": {
        "en": "Head back downstairs, climb the ladder on the north-east side of the castle to get to the 2nd floor. Investigate the suit of armour.",
        "es": "Vuelve a bajar, sube por la escalera de mano en el lado noreste del castillo para llegar a la 2ª planta. Investiga la armadura."
      },
      "chatOptions": []
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "indent": 0,
      "section": "Ambassador Spanfipple",
      "text": {
        "en": "Go downstairs back to ground floor, then head to the east side to investigate the suit of armour.",
        "es": "Baja de nuevo a la planta baja y dirígete al lado este para investigar la armadura."
      },
      "chatOptions": [
        "1. Trick"
      ]
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "indent": 0,
